## reg

Specifies the address and size of a register block or memory region belonging to the device. Encoded as `<address size>` pairs according to the parent's `#address-cells` and `#size-cells`.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    compatible = "qcom,geni-uart";
    reg = <0x00880000 0x200>;
};
```
